{"tid":1924032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"灰到盡但係生活永遠都繼續 冇時間俾你停","createTime":"2020-03-13T12:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T20:29:18.000Z","uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"522765e677b920f375d1c81c548100fa78238134","tid":1924032,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"冇方法去令到自己唔開心<br />\n唔知幾時啲唔開心先會散<br />\n灰到盡但係又未灰到想死<br />\n啲負面就每日屈喺心入面<br />\n究竟點先可以解決呢樣野<br />\n好想乜都擺低唔做靜一靜<br />\n但係又冇咁既機會去自摺 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5825d97c7f6452cfd3d0c8d814d7360d24951f13","tid":1924032,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:12:00.000Z","msg":"或者係已經灰到個人死咁濟 得返個肉體on99唔知做乜咁 <br />\n坐唔安食唔落 搵唔到自己真係可以乜都擺低晒既位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164a572563a4cdca01d9a864d09fff5b9ff2936d","tid":1924032,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"唔開心到自己都唔知係為乜唔開心 因為唔開心都乜都攞返出嚟諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341dadc6ab23747866c1ffde5c3c8cd2c816eb35","tid":1924032,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"靈魂死咗肉體未死每日行屍走肉咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8931f15c74820a0878759f9415a300b7dc630b90","ti